从今年秋天开始，FaceTime 将可用于 Apple TV 4K 设备。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> FaceTime 是 tvOS 17 的主要亮点，但不是唯一的改进。该公司重新设计了控制中心，使其更加直观，更重要的是，增加了“查找我的遥控器”支持。只需在您的手机、平板电脑或电脑上使用 Siri 即可找到任何恶作剧的 Apple TV 遥控器。 Apple 还指出，Cisco 的 Webex 和 Zoom 等视频会议应用程序将于今年晚些时候在 tvOS 上推出。</p><p></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/facetime-is-coming-to-apple-tv-182616297.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/facetime-is-coming-to-apple-tv-182616297.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 470fe02b-e819-4fab-a25e-520f11e58bb4</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 05 Jun 2023 18:26:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1685989949</ingested><modified> 2023-06-05T18:32:33+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="675" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/d7a751f0-03cd-11ee-bafe-64583ec6cced" width="1200"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="675" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/d7a751f0-03cd-11ee-bafe-64583ec6cced" width="1200"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:cr