s-anc-and-transparency-to-your-environment-181218028.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apples-adaptive-audio-for-airpods-tunes-anc-and-transparency-to-your-environment-181218028.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> e02e3f3c-64b1-44f7-ab18-6badb34377f2</guid><dc:creator>威尔尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 05 Jun 2023 18:12:18 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1685991677</ingested><modified> 2023-06-05T19:01:22+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/8ab3aee0-03cb-11ee-9bcd-c44f92a494df" width="1280"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/8ab3aee0-03cb-11ee-9bcd-c44f92a494df" width="1280"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Apple]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Craig Federighi playing a triple-necked guitar]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Craig Federighi with a guitar]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The Apple Watch embraces widgets again in watchOS 10]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>当 watchOS 10 到来时，您的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/apple-watch/">Apple Watch</a>可能看起来会大不相同。 <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-is-reportedly-redesigning-watchos-around-widgets-162720331.html">正如预期的那样，</a>该公司正在对智能手表用户界面进行大修，作为固件迄今为止最大更新之一的一部分。</p><p>你可能还记得，最初的 Apple Watch 用户界面部分是<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2015-04-30-apple-watch-review.html">围绕 Glances</a>设计的——一个用于不同应用程序和功能的小部件轮播。 Apple 最终放弃了 Glances，将更多的重点放在应用程序上，但现在该公司正在寻求让小部件再次成为 Watch 界面的更大焦点。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/413ea3e0-03cc-11ee-9fd3-4f5e9da21729" style="height:1161px;width:2000px;" alt="WatchOS 10 上的小部件" data-uuid="fb67f728-4ffc-3b8c-af40-bb5c7e96d999"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">苹果</div></figure><p>它的工作方式似乎与<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2017-06-05-apple-watchos-4.html">Apple Watch 上长期以来可用的</a>Siri 表盘类似。但是，这种体验现在可用于任何表盘。您可以旋转 Digital Crown 以访问相关小部件的智能堆栈。计时器、秒表和播客之类的东西在使用时会显示为小部件。您甚至可以拥有一个包含您最喜欢的复杂功能的小部件。</p><p>活动应用程序将很快包含角落快捷方式。您将能够通过旋转表冠查看更多数据。世界时钟应用程序也正在更新。它将具有动态背景颜色，以帮助反映不同时区的时间，当您在世界不同地方有朋友、家人或同事时，这可能会派上用场。</p><p> watchOS 10 中有两个新的钟面。一个名为 Palette 的钟面将以多彩的方式显示时间。另一张脸是史努比和伍德斯托克。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/889386a0-03ce-11ee-bfff-7f20a409ad3d" style="height:1161px;width:2000px;" alt="watchOS10 上的骑行应用" data-uuid="fe8dc01a-d3b9-3b32-9923-a006705c6943"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">苹果</div></figure><p>骑自行车的人可能会对 WatchOS 10 中即将推出的更新感到满意。您将能够连接到蓝牙自行车传感器，并在骑自行车时查看功率和心率数据。您的手表也可以估算您的功能阈值功率。您的 Watch 追踪的骑行活动将自动显示在您的 iPhone 上。</p><p> Compass 应用程序也进行了升级，因为它将自动创建两个新的航点。第一个会在您最后一次建立蜂窝连接的估计位置放置一个图钉，这对于您远足并需要拨打电话或查看消息时很有用。同样，您的手表将能够放置一个最后的紧急呼叫航点。 This will show roughly where you last had access to any carrier&#39;s network so you can make an emergency call if needed. A new Elevation view will use altimeter data to provide a 3D view of saved waypoints, while folks in the US will be able to access a topographic map. You&#39;ll be able to search for trailheads and trails nearby and view details such as trail length, type and difficulty. </p><p></p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/129ce5d0-03cf-11ee-bbff-e54ae6fbd0b9" style="height:1161px;width:2000px;" alt="Compass app on watchOS 10" data-uuid="09d45727-18f2-3f9c-aac5-ce9408e6276c"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">苹果</div></figure><p>The Mindfulness app will include a feature that allows you to log your emotions and moods by rotating the Digital Crown. Apple <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Apple;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4130e2f0-a14f-4c5e-bdab-cd52ac7d8e79&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Apple&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAR7yHQh5nRcFjWKKREydAizhzNrDgVxIj8A_l3iTnEqv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fnewsroom%2F2023%2F06%2Fintroducing-watchos-10-a-milestone-update-for-apple-watch%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">says</a> that users can &quot;scroll through engaging, multidimensional shapes to choose how they are feeling, select what is having the biggest impact on them and describe their feelings.&quot; Through the Health app on iPhone and iPad, you&#39;ll be able to access insights that can help you deduce the factors that are affecting your mental health, Apple says. The Apple Watch will also soon have a feature that can track how much time wearers are spending outdoors in an attempt to <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-kid-friendly-features-reduce-eye-strain-wwdc-182620428.html">reduce the risk of nearsightedness</a> .</p><p> Elsewhere, you&#39;ll be able to view a FaceTime video message on your Watch and join Group FaceTime audio. The Medications app can deliver additional reminders if you don&#39;t say you&#39;ve taken your medication within 30 minutes of the scheduled time.</p><p> As for Apple Fitness+, you&#39;ll soon be able to access a custom workout or meditation schedule that fits your needs. Stacks is a feature that&#39;s essentially a playlist for Apple Fitness+. You can use it to line up multiple workouts and meditations that you can run through back-to-back. In addition, there&#39;s a feature called Audio Focus that will let you increase the volume of either the trainers&#39; voices or the music.</p><p> On top of all that, Apple is making some tweaks to the physical controls. Pressing the side button will open the Control Center at any time. Double pressing the Digital Crown will take you back to your recently used apps.</p><p> Developers will have access to a beta of watchOS 10 starting today and a public beta will arrive next month. Apple will release watchOS 10 publicly this fall. You&#39;ll need an Apple Watch Series 4 or later to use the new version of the OS.</p><p> <em>Follow all of the news from Apple&#39;s WWDC 2023</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/wwdc-2023/"><em>right here</em></a> <em>.</em></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/the-apple-watch-embraces-widgets-again-in-watchos-10-180838970.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-apple-watch-embraces-widgets-again-in-watchos-10-180838970.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 63703d27-3627-4fbe-a936-ac66ed28580b</guid><dc:creator> Kris Holt</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 05 Jun 2023 18:08:38 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1685991997</ingested><modified> 2023-06-05T19:06:45+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><catego